{
  "texts": [
    "This means that younger students relate to higher performance in AI-assisted writing activities.",
    "This finding transpires because the age of students relates to their generation which is called the Genz Era or they are commonly referred to as the fully \"digitally native\" generation.",
    "This means that students at this age grew up with social media and smartphones.",
    "Thus, they are technologically adept.",
    "This implies that students are fascinated to use or navigate applications efficiently since they are exposed to technology."
  ]
}